STUDENT.observations: This was fun. Some tasks were a lot easier than others. I wish my partner or partner and I had formed more one letter or shape symbols to help us out because I really struggled to understand more complicated drawn messages and my brain had trouble both understanding and keeping track of longer messages for the same task - like a word vs a shape drawn with a car. We did form an understanding for easier maps so if knew if he made the message simple or demonstration simple than our goal was probably also simple. We also had signs for when it was all of something or just one, 2 or 3 of something - that worked pretty well. I think we struggled a little later because we did so well on simple tasks that we didn't always need to develop symbols for things that could have helped us on more complicated tasks.
